Package com.illiasalohub.movieapp.model

Class StatisticsResult

java.lang.Object
com.illiasalohub.movieapp.model.StatisticsResult
public class StatisticsResult extends Object
Encapsulates the results of various statistical analyses of the user movies. This class is used for information about total user statistics such as the count of watched movies, the oldest and newest movies, the most watched director, and ratings statistics.
